@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8000

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
Accept: application/json

### Text Search
POST {{baseUrl}}/search/text
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "query": "중3 국어 문학 비유법"
}

